README:
This library uses Hopcroft algorithm to minimize Coq file objects.
It is adaptable to any OCaml structure easily.

Article describing the algorithm and its justification (in French):
http://hal.archives-ouvertes.fr/hal-00779752/

Hopcroft implementation is taken from:
http://arxiv.org/abs/0802.2826
description: Small library to compute maximal sharing of OCaml datastructures.
